write by python 2.7

install PySide and markdown module:
pip install PySide
pip install markdown

use python's markdown module to parse *.md/*.markdown file, and show it in pyside's qwebview widget by setHtml() function real time.

use WriteHtml xx/xx.html command to write html file.
use WriteImg xx/xx.jpg/png command to write image file.

add python markdown's table extesion.

you can create table like this:

 xxxx | xxxx | xxxx
 -----|:----:|:-----
 aaaaa|aaaaaa|aaaaaa

:-----: center align
:------ left align
------: right align
